0.name: Before the Gate
desc: "   There is a large gate rising out of the forest through which several wagons
could pass side by side.  You notice that the forest is cleared back somewhat
from the wall that disappears into the distance both north and east from the
gate.  The arch above the gate is emblazoned with the emblem of the city of
Arador.  The mouth of the tower seems to be filled with spikes that force the
traffic into the darkness of the gate tunnel.
